public class LimitedReinsertOverflowTreatment
extends Object
implements OverflowTreatment
    Limited reinsertions, as proposed by the R*-Tree: For each real insert, allow reinsertions to happen only once per level.
    Since:
    0.5.0
    Author:
    Erich Schubert
